FBIS4-15229 "drsov067_a_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-067 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin Said To Approve Military Bases in CIS, Latvia Yeltsin Said To Approve Military Bases in CIS, Latvia LD0604143394 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1330 GMT 6 Apr 94 LD0604143394 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin has approved a Defense Ministry proposal on creating Russian Armed Forces military bases on the territory of CIS countries and Latvia to ensure their common security and also to test new weapons and military equipment. The president has instructed the Foreign and Defense Ministries to hold talks with these states in order to achieve the necessary agreements.
